  <Fragment slot="what-this-is">
    <p>Payroll involves more than paying staff. It also includes deductions, CRA remittances, records, year-end forms, and ongoing compliance tasks that need to be handled consistently.</p>
    <p>For small businesses, payroll often becomes a recurring admin burden because it has little margin for error and must be done on schedule regardless of what else is happening in the business.</p>
